insert  into `antalk_details`(`antalk_id`,`antalk_date`,`antalk_description`) values (1,'2013-01-04','<ul>\r\n<li>Discussed regarding the completed tasks for this week and follow up tasks for next week of an individual.</li>\r\n<li>Congratulated Mallikarjun and Harish for completing one year of service at Proton.</li>\r\n<li>Mallikarjun and Harish shared their experience and journey of 1 year at Proton.</li>\r\n<li>Conveyed that the First Aid kit has been upgraded with the necessary things. If required, please contact Angel - Receptionist cum Telecaller</li>\r\n</ul>'),(2,'2013-01-11','<ul>\r\n<li>Discussed regarding the completed tasks for this week and follow up tasks for next week of an individual</li>\r\n<li>Discussed regarding the efforts to be put up for starting Mobile Application development and as well as on Business Development.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Discussed about the changes in the infrastructure</li>\r\n</ul>'),(3,'2013-01-18','<p>Antalk session was held from 5:30 PM to 6:30 PM on 18th Jan 2013. The points dicussed are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Regarding the completed tasks and follow up tasks of an individual.</li>\r\n<li>Regarding the tchnical issues of Star Program in iConnect</li>\r\n<li>Regarding the project completion dates where the teams should stick on to the targets dates in delivering the projetcs irrespective of whether it is internal project or extenal project.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(4,'2013-01-25','<p>Antalk Session was held from 5:30 PM to 6:10 OM on 25th Jan 2013. The points discussed are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Regarding the completed tasks and follow up tasks of an individual</li>\r\n<li>Adopting the practise of recording the meetings with the clinet and the points discussed</li>\r\n<li>Given the clarification regarding the half day leave that an employee availing morning session leave should be present at office before 2PM. If not, it is considered as half day LOP</li>\r\n<li>Given suggestions and guidelines to Impact Team</li>\r\n</ul>'),(5,'2013-02-01','<p>Antalk Session was held from 5:30 PM to 6:30 PM. The points discussed are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Regarding the completed tasks and follow up tasks of every individual</li>\r\n<li>Declared Ingenious team as stars of the month for successfully achieving 50 projects mile stone, given certificates and trophy, applauded and congratulated</li>\r\n<li>Introduced new department &nbsp;by the Management namely ISAAC which is into Server and Networking Solutions</li>\r\n<li>Reviewed the performance of all the departments</li>\r\n<li>Adieu to Rupesh Kumar by the whole Proton team as he will be relieved by 5th Feb (Tuesday)</li>\r\n</ul>'),(6,'2013-02-08','<p>Antalk Session was held from 5:30 PM to 6:30 PM. The points discussed are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Regarding the completed tasks of current week and follow up tasks of next week of an individual.</li>\r\n<li>Welcomed Mr. Vijesh Kumar who has joined us as Field Sales Representative on 4th Feb 2013</li>\r\n<li>Thoughts and ideas in improving and expanding the Ingenious team</li>\r\n<li>Reviewed the performance of all the departments individually by the Management</li>\r\n<li>Regarding the expectations by the Management from the teams</li>\r\n</ul>'),(7,'2013-02-15','<p>Antalk Session was held from 5:30 PM to 6:15 PM. The points discussed are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Regarding the completed tasks of current week and follow up tasks of next week of an individual.</li>\r\n<li>Implementation of Proton Employee ID/Access card form and filing the same.</li>\r\n<li>Clarified from HR Department that if an employee wants to leave early for the day, a mail has to send to the Reporting Manager marking a copy to HR seeking for the permission.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(8,'2013-02-22','<p>Antalk Session was held from 5:30 PM to 6:30 PM. The points discussed are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Regarding the completed tasks of current week and follow up tasks of next week of an individual.</li>\r\n<li>Congratulated Samaresh and Sowmya for completing one year at Proton</li>\r\n<li>Regarding the annual performance appraisal of an individual starting from 25th Feb by HR Department who has completed one year of service at Proton. Adding to this, it was clearly clarified that the increment will be based on individual performance, handling and completing the tasks, taking the risks, etc.</li>\r\n<li>Regarding the closure of the projects by the team lead that Shopmykart and Heera has to be closed by Feb 2013 end, NRack and sriRam by next week. No more extension of time will be allowed. Adding to this, it has been decided and declared that henceforth only one resource (Only Yousuf) from Impact team will be shared to Ingenious team for their projects.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(9,'2013-03-01','<p>Antalk Session was held from 5:30 PM to 5:50 PM. The points discussed are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Regarding the completed tasks of current week and follow up tasks of next week of an individual</li>\r\n<li>No Star for the month of March</li>\r\n<li>First Aid kit has been upgraded with all the necessary things. Kindly contact Receptionist or HR Department for any emergency of First Aid Kit</li>\r\n</ul>'),(10,'2013-03-08','<p>Antalk Session was held from 5:30 PM to 6:45 PM. The points discussed are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Regarding the completed tasks of current week and follow up tasks of next week of an individual</li>\r\n<li>Regarding the project management and planning&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Regarding the future plans to make ISAAC grow</li>\r\n<li>Regarding the internal communication between the employees as there is a lack of communication between the employee regarding the sharing of work and taking the help of others to complete the work on time when required</li>\r\n<li>Regarding the responsibilities and taking the ownership of the work to complete it on time</li>\r\n</ul>'),(11,'2013-03-15','<p>Antalk Session was held from 5:30 PM to 6:15 PM. The points discussed are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Regarding the completed tasks of current week and follow up tasks of next week of an individual</li>\r\n<li>Congratulated Dinesh Sir for completing 500 days of training</li>\r\n<li>Congratulated Dinesh Sir for being awarded by the all India Achievers Fundation on 9th March At Delhi</li>\r\n<li>Regarding the new upcoming project of building Case Studey for IBM new hires through Oracle</li>\r\n<li>Regarding the new upcoming project of content development and training at Vietnam on Siebel CRM</li>\r\n<li>Regarding the necessity of JSF training for 2-3 days for Impact team</li>\r\n<li>Closures of the projects by Inpact and Ingenious teams</li>\r\n</ul>'),(12,'2013-03-22','<p>Antalk Session was held from <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>5:30 PM to 6:20 PM</strong></span>. The points discussed are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Regarding the current week\'s completed tasks and next week\'s follow up tasks of an individual</li>\r\n<li>New project name <strong>New Comfort Engineerig</strong> for Ingenious of Dynamic Website</li>\r\n<li>Performance and analysis of all the teams individually with reports of quarter and year 2012-13; Financial yearly analysis is pending and has been postponed to next week</li>\r\n<li>Implementation of<strong> Ticketing System</strong> integrating with STS</li>\r\n<li>Focusing on International Database and Internet marketing and also set up of infrastucture for the same</li>\r\n<li>Future plans of ISAAC like VAT regisrtation and also using the sales team (3 people) by making the sales team a geneal sales team for Proton (not only for Ingenious)</li>\r\n<li>Permission request, Leave application, comp off request, etc are not considered for the approval if sent as a mail instead by iconnect.</li>\r\n<li>When applying for half day leave, have to clearly mention whether it is morning session or noon session</li>\r\n<li>In the Login and Attendance register, check before you sign whether signing in correct place or not</li>\r\n<li>If not able to sign in Login register because of Client meeting, etc., it has to be signed the very next consecutive day itself&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Change in the<em><strong> Antalk Session</strong> </em>- On last Friday of every month, will discuss regarding entire month\'s tasks completed along with the current week\'s completed tasks (Over view of the entire month\'s work).</li>\r\n</ul>'),(13,'2013-03-29','<p>Antalk Session was held from 5:30 PM to 6:30 PM. The points are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Discussed regarding the completed tasks of the current week and follow up tasks for the next week of an individual</li>\r\n<li>Brief discussion regarding the tasks completed in the current month of an individual</li>\r\n<li>Discussed regarding concentrating on the<em><strong> Internet Marketing</strong></em> and working towards it</li>\r\n<li>Started up the work and operations according to the plan and targets in improving the ISAAC Department</li>\r\n<li>Two more new projects to Ingenious team, <em><strong>Brightway School </strong></em>and<em><strong> Buddies Books Pvt Lt</strong></em></li>\r\n<li>Stepped into the direct <strong>domain registration</strong> by Proton</li>\r\n</ul>'),(14,'2013-04-05','<p>Antalk Session was held from 5:30 PM to 6:00 PM. The points are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Discussed regarding the completed tasks of the current week and follow up tasks for the next week of an individual</li>\r\n<li>Applauded for the closure of Heera Advertising project</li>\r\n<li>Applauded for hosting STS - test version for a week and any clarifications regarding the same should be addressed to Nandish</li>\r\n</ul>'),(15,'2013-04-12','<p>Antalk Session was held from 5:30 PM to 6:00 PM. The points are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Discussed regarding the completed tasks of the current week and follow up tasks for the next week of an individual</li>\r\n<li>Discussed regarding the closures of the projects and technical issues</li>\r\n</ul>'),(16,'2013-04-19','<p>Antalk Session was held from 5:30 PM to 6:30 PM. The points are:</p>\