:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Regarding the completed tasks of the current week and follow up tasks for the next week of an individual</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Congratulated Dinesh sir for completing 700 days of training successfully</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Appreciated Samaresh for the session on Word Press</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Explained the Dress Code Policy to be followed as most of them are not following the dress code</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Cleared the RH status of the employees as any employee can avail only two RH in a calendar year and given the status of all the employees respectively</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Decoration has been assigned to Samaresh and saranya on 20</span><sup style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; line-height: 150%;\">th</sup><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\"> Oct for the occasion of Diwali</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(92,'2014-10-22','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 24.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Garamond\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Antalk Session was held from&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">5:30 PM to 6:00 PM</span></strong>. Following are the points discussed:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Regarding the completed tasks of the current week and follow up tasks for the next week of an individual</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Conveyed the greetings to the team for the occasion of Diwali on behalf of the Management</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Discussed about the closures for the next week which are high in priority</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">The Management is working on focusing to take Proton to a different level by capturing the market in South Africa</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Started working on the other Business Unit by initiating a direct vendor registration process with Oracle SSI by the Management to source people into Oracle on Proton Payroll&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(93,'2014-10-31','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 24.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Garamond\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Antalk Session was held from&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">5:30 PM to 6:00 PM</span></strong>. Following are the points discussed:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Regarding the completed tasks of the current week and follow up tasks for the next week of an individual</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Two new projects namely Satvic Organic which is an e-commerce project and Rite Equipment Pvt. Ltd is a dynamic website design</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Discussed about the closures for the next week which are h